flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 35: RBAC Authorization Matrix and Access Control Flow

  User[User signs in]
  Token[JWT with role and permissions]
  Request[Protected API request]
  Route[Endpoint requires role scope]
  Guard[Roles guard @Roles]
  Check{Role and scope allowed?}

  Allow[Allow handler execution]
  Deny[Return 403 forbidden]
  DomainCheck{Resource ownership or domain rule passes?}

  VendorOK[Vendor can manage own products]
  FinanceOK[Finance admin can release escrow and process disbursement]
  ModOK[Content mod or super admin can moderate content]
  SuperAdmin[Super admin can access all admin paths]

  Audit[(Append immutable audit log)]
  Matrix[Role set\nSuper Admin, Vendor, Buyer, Support, Delivery, Affiliate, Finance Admin, Content Mod]

  User --> Token --> Request --> Route --> Guard --> Check
  Check -- No --> Deny --> Audit
  Check -- Yes --> DomainCheck
  DomainCheck -- No --> Deny
  DomainCheck -- Yes --> Allow --> Audit

  Allow --> VendorOK
  Allow --> FinanceOK
  Allow --> ModOK
  Allow --> SuperAdmin
  Matrix -.applies to.-> Guard
